n \in \mathbb {N}
x \in \mathbb{R}
x^{2n}+x^{2n-1}+...x+1
x<-1
x+1<0
x^{2i-1}(x+1)>0
x^{2n}+x^{2n-1}+...x+1= \sum_{i=1}^n (x^{2i} + x^{2i-1}) +1=\sum_{i=1}^n x^{2i-1}(x+1) +1> 0
 -1\leq x <0
x+1\geq0
x^{2i-2}(x+1) \geq 0
x^{2n}+x^{2n-1}+...x+1= x^{2n}+ \sum_{i=1}^n (x^{2i-1} + x^{2i-2}) =x^{2n}+\sum_{i=1}^n x^{2i-2}(x+1) \geq x^{2n}+ 0>0
x\geq 0
